{"tid":790491,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[擔心] 求神拜佛, 子瑜BB千祈唔好屎忽痕去印度","createTime":"2018-08-23T04:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T16:47:20.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"977a0e04aaa66bf20be29ef3cf17a2adddda4631","tid":790491,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:59:42.000Z","msg":"子瑜「33秒舊短片」紅爆印度！　《索爾》導演都轉PO：熱搜體質正常發揮<br />\n<br />\n...一名男網友7月底在PTT「TWICE版」PO文，透露在台灣工作的印度工程師好友某天拿著一張照片，向他打聽子瑜是不是正港台灣人，他好奇印度好友怎麼突然問起，一問之下才知道子瑜最近在印度爆紅，且全團就只紅子瑜一個，他相當意外以印度男人的審美觀，竟然會煞到子瑜，才發文想尋求子瑜為何在印度爆紅的原因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3502/e3502732.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3502%2Fe3502732.jpg&h=04f20e83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3502/e3502729.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3502%2Fe3502729.jpg&h=4ee30696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有粉絲解答其實是印度知名的某八卦娛樂IG分享了今年2月子瑜在偶像運動會上射箭比賽的影片，累積了143萬人次觀看，讓子瑜一夕爆紅，還上了當地新聞，網路上甚至出現許多搭配印度音樂的子瑜影片，其中一支還有破萬讚數，一度還有人以為她是射箭選手，不少粉絲笑說：「推子瑜熱搜體質正常發揮。」<br />\n<br />\n事實上，子瑜在2016年參加射箭比賽，放箭時弓弦撥起頭髮，讓她的一頭秀髮隨之飛散，美麗的一瞬間被製成動畫瘋傳，還紅到好萊塢，連《雷神索爾3》的導演泰卡瓦提提和《麻辣賤諜》導演保羅費格都在推特轉發，連西班牙都曾風靡過一陣子。<br />\n<br />\n得知子瑜在印度爆紅，許多網友開心表示「習慣就好。子瑜的日常」、「子瑜這孩子真的很神奇」、「推子瑜熱搜體質」、「子瑜的五官好像符合各國審美標準」、「自體發光的子瑜」。<br />\n<br />\n子瑜是許多人心中的理想型，連前輩Apink娜恩都超愛她，在看後輩團體的表演影像時，看到子瑜「真的太漂亮了」，曾在錄製《偶像明星運動會》時遇過本人，當時覺得彷彿看到剛出道時的自己，「沒有什麼話、很安靜，從那時候就對子瑜特別關心。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1240983\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1240983&d=h7c0o%2BmwdMUlfomTdpq4wYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=089da812\" target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1240983</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n否則莫講話處女膜, <br />\n耳膜鼻膜眼角膜都屌穿呀~!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade291f6bbe86755481f38f62bd6fc5d71fa14ae","tid":790491,"uid":76098,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:02:00.000Z","msg":"印度班生番計我話連j子瑜既資格都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a9c56f3e25b711009c7dc520613cbb3727f6fa","tid":790491,"uid":156592,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:03:06.000Z","msg":"放心，佢喺我屋企好安全"},{"pid":"fe6cf03fe028c0d5ba4e2ca10113635725384362","tid":790491,"uid":75655,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ade291f6bbe86755481f38f62bd6fc5d71fa14ae","tid":790491,"uid":76098,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:02:00.000Z","msg":"印度班生番計我話連j子瑜既資格都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:05:00.000Z","msg":"一落機，比印度佬百人斬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,無限中出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a05061f203a097ea903d244ab1630f1182ed64","tid":790491,"uid":21247,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:07:09.000Z","msg":"我條女唔到你管"},{"pid":"43f46924dc7dbe0404a2ad0c92205eef9df9a422","tid":790491,"uid":21423,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:14:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00883e27beb1358fdc8624d3960bf4c1b805cfcb","tid":790491,"uid":198998,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"43f46924dc7dbe0404a2ad0c92205eef9df9a422","tid":790491,"uid